Name: Car Wash Simulator
About the game: We all know that a clean car drives better. :) Car Wash Simulator is racing-simulator game which includes the next jobs: taxi driver & washing sports cars. Over time, the car gets dirty due to dirtyroads. Therefore, you must always keep it clean, because you will not have a request from customers. So, you have to pay close attention at your car. Good luck with your work and be carefull on the roads. Game Features : - 10 levels - 10 supercars - Dirty roads, pretentious customers - Gps
